    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This is a good, honest car that presents well and should make a solid driver for someone looking for something enjoyable and usable without paying top dollar for a fully show-level example. It appears to have been cared for reasonably well, with the kind of light cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections you would expect from a well-kept used car rather than a freshly restored one. Overall, it should suit a buyer who wants a nice, presentable car they can enjoy and improve over time if desired.",
