      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for a buyer who values affordability and practicality over perfection. A great opportunity for a commuter, first-time buyer, or anyone looking for inexpensive transportation with room to make it their own.",
