    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest budget-friendly car that\u2019s ready for someone who wants affordable wheels or a solid little project. It\u2019s not perfect and shows its age, but it has plenty of life left for the right buyer who appreciates a straightforward deal. If you\u2019re after cheap transportation without spending a fortune, this could be a great fit. Priced to sell and offered by someone who believes in being upfront and easy to deal with.",
